Title: 
    Using Message Queue to Build Scalable and Highly Available System
Abstract:
    In this presentation, i will introduce about rubichat.com, a realtime communication service
    and the solution using RabbitMQ to make it easy to scale out and highly available.
    I will also discuss about how to apply this solution to some specific systems.
Final abstract:
    In this presentation, i will introduce rubichat.com, a realtime communication service 
    as well as the method to scale out and to make the system highly available.
    I will also discuss the ability to apply the proposed method to other distributed systems in general.

